snippet.title: Maestro: The Masterclass Trailer
snippet.description:
Step on the podium and become a true orchestra conductor in Maestro: The Masterclass!

A unique VR experience, developed by a French studio to make the world of orchestral conducting accessible to everyone!

Available now on #metaquest2 : https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4813149252124417/
